name: WunksV2
description:
THE FIRST FULLY WOMEN THEMED PUNK DERIVATIVE. 

We are Wunks. Women Punks with Purpose. Wunks are leveling the playing field and changing the game with unique utility, benefits, and community funds. Wunks pave the way for equity of access in the NFT space. We, Wunks, are here to stay with our own style and rocking a whole lot of pink!

There are 6,000 Wunks in total.

Utility:

- Access to blam.io, a NFT launchpad for generative collections.

- Submit proposals for using the Wunk Community fund

- Access to holder only discord channels

- And so much more
